cpp2html -- History of visible changes.

Copyright (C) 1999, 2000, Lorenzo Bettini <bettini@gnu.org>
See the end for copying conditions.

Please send cpp2html bug reports to bug-cpp2html@gnu.org

Version 1.1

* --header and --footer options added by Xavier Outhier <xouthier@yahoo.fr>,
  that allow to specify files to be included at the beginning and at the 
  end of the generated document. 
* GNU gengetopt is used for command line parsing. 
* hexadecimal and floating point numbers are treated 
  (Tom Hull <thull@kscable.com>). 
* fixed the bug of /* comment in another environment 
  (notified by Michael Gasche <mgasche@datacomm.ch> for java2html)

